00:39:18,915 --> 00:39:23,688
** Or when the valley's**

546
00:39:24,069 --> 00:39:32,136
**Hushed and white with snow**

547
00:39:32,714 --> 00:39:38,606
** 'Tis I'll be here**

548
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:46,977
**In sunshine or in shadow**

549
00:39:48,390 --> 00:39:52,046
** Oh, Danny Boy**

550
00:39:52,295 --> 00:39:56,287
** Oh, Danny Boy**

551
00:39:56,747 --> 00:40:05,025
**I love you so**

552
00:40:18,798 --> 00:40:21,951
**But when ye come**

553
00:40:23,155 --> 00:40:28,484
**And all the flowers
are dying**

554
00:40:29,034 --> 00:40:32,080
**If am dead**

555
00:40:32,638 --> 00:40:38,819
**As dead I well maybe**

556
00:40:40,871 --> 00:41:00,296
-[Struggling, Grunting]

557
