Miller's Crossing.
-I didn't do-- Tom! Tom!

775
00:57:02,127 --> 00:57:04,561
- Lock him up.
Jesus! Are you part of this?

776
00:57:04,630 --> 00:57:06,825
- Sit still, hymie.
- You can't be part of this.

777
00:57:06,899 --> 00:57:09,561
I think these guys
are gonna whack me!
Tom, you gotta talk to 'em!

778
00:57:09,635 --> 00:57:12,570
- You're giving me a headache,
you little sheeny. Lets go!
- Talk to 'em!

779
00:57:15,541 --> 00:57:17,907
[Bernie]
Get me outta here!

780
00:57:17,976 --> 00:57:20,444
Oh, Tommy.!

781
00:57:20,512 --> 00:57:22,537
- [ Frankie ]
Get him outta here!
- [ Bernie ] Frankie!

782
00:57:22,614 --> 00:57:25,515
- Come on! Come on!
- [ Blubbering ]

783
00:57:27,886 --> 00:57:29,979
- Tic-Tac!
- Quiet him down!

784
00:57:30,055 --> 00:57:31,989
Uuh!

785
00:57:32,057 --> 00:57:34,184
- Get up, you skel!
- [ Groans ]

786
00:57:34,259 --> 00:57:36,352
- Come on.
- Frankie, no!

787
00:57:36,428 --> 00:57:39,886
- Get up, you son of a bitch.
- Frank-- Aah!

788
00:57:39,965 --> 00:57:42,559
- Oh, Frankie!
- Get up, you kike!

789
00:57:42,634 --> 00:57:46,536
[Tic-Tac]
Okay, take him in the woods
and whack him.

790
00:57:46,605 --> 00:57:48,835
- What?
- That's right.

791
00:57:48,907 --> 00:57:51,876
The boss wants you to do it.
Make sure youre with the good guys.

792
00:57:51,944 --> 00:57:54,777
- You know how to do this, right?
- You little yid! Get up!

793
00:57:54,847 --> 00:57:56,940
Ya gotta remember
to put one in his brain.

794
00:57:57,015 --> 00:58:00,041
Your first shot puts him down.
Then you put one in his brain.

795
00:58:00,118 --> 00:58:02,211
Then he's dead.
Then we go home.

796
00:58:02,287 --> 00:58:05,848
[Struggling,
Blubbering Continues]

797
00:58:05,924 --> 00:58:08,154
Get up and walk.

798
00:58:08,227 --> 00:58:10,491
I can't get up. I cant get up.

799
00:58:10,562 --> 00:58:14,562
- Get up and walk,
you pissing little yid!
- [Tic-Tac]Lets go!

800
00:58:35,654 --> 00:58:38,714
Tommy, you can't do this.
You don't bump guys.

801
00:58:38,790 --> 00:58:41,122
You're not like
those animals back there.

802
00:58:43,528 --> 00:58:45,758
It's not right, Tom.

803
00:58:45,831 --> 00:58:48,265
They can't make us do this.

804
00:58:48,333 --> 00:58:52,333
It's a wrong situation.
They can't make us
different people than we are.

805
00:58:52,638 --> 00:58:54,572
We're not muscle.
I never killed anybody.

806
00:58:54,640 --> 00:58:57,234
I used a little information
for a chisel, that's all.

807
00:58:57,309 --> 00:58:59,971
It's my nature, Tom.
I can't help it.

808
00:59:00,045 --> 00:59:03,879
Somebody hands me an angle,
I play it. I don't deserve
to die for that.

809
00:59:03,949 --> 00:59:05,883
Do you think I do?

810
00:59:07,619 --> 00:59:11,316
I'm just a grifter.
Huh, Tom? I'm a nobody!

811
00:59:11,390 --> 00:59:14,882
But I tell you what--
I never crossed a friend.

812
00:59:14,960 --> 00:59:17,326
I never killed anybody,
I never crossed a friend.

813
00:59:17,396 --> 00:59:19,330
We're not like those animals.

814
00:59:19,398 --> 00:59:21,332
This is not us.

815
00:59:21,400 --> 00:59:24,062
[ Stammering ]
This is a dream!

816
00:59:24,136 --> 00:59:27,299
It's a dream, Tommy!
I'm praying to you!

817
00:59:27,372 --> 00:59:29,340
I can't die.

818
00:59:29,408 --> 00:59:31,342
I can't die...

819
00:59:31,410 --> 00:59:35,141
out here in the woods
like a dumb animal.

820
00:59:35,213 --> 00:59:37,647
In the woods like a dumb animal!

821
00:59:37,716 --> 00:59:40,685
Like a--
Like a dumb animal!

822
00:59:40,752 --> 00:59:44,483
I cant--
I cant-- I can't die
out here in the woods...

823
00:59:44,556 --> 00:59:47,150
like a dumb animal.
[ Sobbing ]

824
00:59:47,225 --> 00:59:50,626
I can't... die!

825
00:59:54,433 --> 00:59:56,367
I'm praying to you.

