01:00:08,613 --> 01:00:11,309
Look in your heart.

830
01:00:11,383 --> 01:00:14,750
Im praying to you!

831
01:00:14,820 --> 01:00:16,913
Look in your heart!

832
01:00:18,390 --> 01:00:21,587
Im praying to you!
Look in your heart.

833
01:00:21,660 --> 01:00:24,788
Im praying to you!

834
01:00:24,863 --> 01:00:28,863
Look in your heart!
Look in your heart!

835
01:00:29,234 --> 01:00:31,498
You can't kill me.

836
01:00:31,570 --> 01:00:34,471
- Look in your heart.
- [Gun Fires]

837
01:00:49,721 --> 01:00:52,713
- Tommy--
- Shut up. You're dead. Get me?

838
01:00:55,327 --> 01:00:57,921
I understand. I'm dead.

839
01:00:57,996 --> 01:01:00,430
- God bless you.
-Shut up.

840
01:01:00,499 --> 01:01:03,900
You have to disappear for good.
No one can see you.
No one can know.

841
01:01:03,969 --> 01:01:07,234
- God bless you.
-Go somewhere no one knows you.

842
01:01:07,305 --> 01:01:10,763
Anyone sees you,
you really are dead.
You're not my problem anymore.

843
01:01:10,842 --> 01:01:13,276
Of course not.
You've done your share. Thank you.

844
01:01:13,345 --> 01:01:16,314
- Don't worry. I understand.
-Shut up. Shut up.

845
01:01:16,381 --> 01:01:20,010
- Thank you.
- Shut up. Get out of here
before I change my mind.

846
01:01:20,085 --> 01:01:22,553
[ Whispers ]
God bless you.

847
01:01:40,172 --> 01:01:42,106
[Frankie Coughs]

848
01:01:45,077 --> 01:01:47,807
[ Chattering, Laughing ]

849
01:01:53,652 --> 01:01:55,586
[ Frankie ]
Put one in his brain?

850
01:01:56,755 --> 01:01:58,848
- Yeah.
- [ Tic-Tac ]
Atta boy.

851
01:02:04,629 --> 01:02:06,859
[ Laughing ]

852
01:02:13,672 --> 01:02:15,606
[Streetcar Rumbling]

853
01:02:15,674 --> 01:02:17,972
Mink? Tom Reagan.
Where you been?

854
01:02:18,043 --> 01:02:20,136
[Mink On Phone, Indistinct]

855
01:02:24,416 --> 01:02:27,283
Will you look?
Eddie Dane's been looking for you.

856
01:02:27,352 --> 01:02:29,286
- Bernie's dead.
-Jesus Christ!

857
01:02:29,354 --> 01:02:33,354
Stop wailing and listen to me.
Caspar knows you were
in on selling out his fix.

858
01:02:33,692 --> 01:02:35,956
- Who the hell
gave him that idea?
- Heh!

859
01:02:36,027 --> 01:02:39,622
- I guess I gave him that idea.
Sorry. It just slipped out.
- What are you trying to do?

860
01:02:39,698 --> 01:02:42,633
Shut up and let me talk.
You lay low till Caspar
cools off.

861
01:02:42,701 --> 01:02:46,701
Then tell him the Dane was in
on the sellout, and I'll
make Caspar go easy on you.

862
01:02:47,539 --> 01:02:50,474
- You got me into this mess.
- That's right, I got you into this.

863
01:02:50,542 --> 01:02:54,103
-Just remember, Mink, I'm the
only one who can get you out.
- Wait a minute, Tom.

864
01:02:54,179 --> 01:02:57,046
Waah! Uuh!

865
01:03:03,955 --> 01:03:07,948
Hello, Terry.
Getting out the vote?

866
01:03:08,026 --> 01:03:12,026
A message from Leo.
Leo says if youre smart
you'll sit this one out,

867
01:03:13,732 --> 01:03:16,223
not that he cares one way
or the other.

868
01:03:16,301 --> 01:03:20,301
Leo says if youre on
the wrong side you take
your chances like anybody else.

869
01:03:20,930 --> 01:03:23,330
Leo says he gives
no special favors, that's all.

870
01:03:23,424 --> 01:03:26,325
Tell Leo he's not God
on the throne.

871
01:03:26,393 --> 01:03:30,022
Hes just a cheap political boss
with more hair tonic than brains.

872
01:03:30,097 --> 01:03:33,692
[ Groans ]
Uhh!

873
01:03:36,337 --> 01:03:38,430
Did Leo say that as well?

874
01:03:38,506 --> 01:03:40,440
No, I said that.

875
01:03:41,609 --> 01:03:44,043
Cross Leo,
next time I'll say plenty.

876
01:03:45,980 --> 01:03:49,980
[Car's Doors Shut,
Departs]

877
01:03:51,285 --> 01:03:54,220
When youre right, you're right.

878
01:03:54,288 --> 01:03:57,587
But you never say,
I told you so.

879
01:03:57,658 --> 01:03:59,751
[Tom]
So what am I right about?

880
01:04:01,162 --> 01:04:03,824
Well, I'll tell you.

881
01:04:03,898 --> 01:04:07,732
But first you gotta promise
not to say I told you so.

882
01:04:07,802 --> 01:04:11,802
I never say that,
and I don't like people who do.

883
01:04:14,575 --> 01:04:16,907
Mink was robbing me
right along with the shmatte.

884
01:04:16,977 --> 01:04:18,911
