We can't find him.

886
01:04:21,348 --> 01:04:23,782
The Dane, hes making
excuses for him.

887
01:04:23,851 --> 01:04:26,285
But personally,
I think you was right.

888
01:04:26,353 --> 01:04:28,981
I think that Mink and Bernie
was in it together.

889
01:04:29,056 --> 01:04:32,492
